occurs inland in 
<collectingRegion box="[691,763,1846,1872]" country="Brazil" name="Bahia" pageId="18" pageNumber="93">Bahia</collectingRegion>
. It inhabits semideciduous seasonal forest and lowland tropical moist forest (
<bibRefCitation author="Gouvea J. B. S. &amp; Mattos Silva L. A. &amp; Hori M." box="[439,669,1883,1909]" pageId="18" pageNumber="93" pagination="1 - 7" refId="ref22172" refString="Gouvea J. B. S., Mattos Silva L. A. &amp; Hori M. 1976 1. Fitogeografia. In: Diagnostico socioeconomico da Regiao cacaueira Vol. 7: 1 - 7. Comissao Executiva do Plano da Lavoura Cacaueira and the Instituto Interamericano de Ciencias Agricolas-OEA., Recursos Florestais, Ilheus." type="journal article" year="1976">
Gouvêa 
<emphasis box="[541,600,1883,1909]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="93">et al.</emphasis>
1976
</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Thomas W. W. &amp; Barbosa M. R. V." box="[680,978,1883,1909]" pageId="18" pageNumber="93" pagination="6 - 20" refId="ref24665" refString="Thomas W. W. &amp; Barbosa M. R. V. 2008. Natural vegetation types in the Atlantic Coastal Forest of Northeastern Brazil. In: Thomas W. W. (ed.) The Atlantic Coastal Forest of Northeastern Brazil. Memoirs of the New York Botanical Garden 100: 6 - 20." type="journal article" year="2008">Thomas &amp; Barbosa 2008</bibRefCitation>
; 
